The USA changes the rules for the receipt of a visa 
The persons must introduce themselves before their discussion with the consulate with the service places to the visa requesting\; Costs are shortened in such a way latencies. 
Starting from 10 January 2011 the procedures for requesting a visa in the message of the United States and in the consulates change. 
With the new procedure most applicants before their discussion in the consulate must have an interview with the service places to the visa requesting (ASC, the initial letters on English). 
The personnel of the ASC takes up the biometric data of the applicant, which are examined by the consulate before the discussion. 
The new procedure has certain advantages for the aspirants, in addition to count: 
Total costs for completion visa sink, because it is any longer necessary date arrangement, which is handed out treatment of the visa request and the transport service to pay with which the document, separately. 
The applicant makes only one payment, which covers the three services. 
The present price remains unchanged: the Gegenwerit to 140 dollar for a tourist visa, 150 dollar for visas with request (including visas for time workers) and 390 dollar for Händer and investors. 
Those, which would like to only extend their visa, do not have to hold a conversation in the consulate, them must only with the nearest ASC introduce itself, where they are taken their documents to submit and their fingerprints. 
Since the biometric data in the ASC are caught up, the applicants, who need a second date for the discussion in the consulate, remain there less time than in former times. 
Those, which request the visa in the consulates of Ciudad Juárez, Monterrey and Nuevo Laredo, do not have to pay the service impact of 26 dollar to no more. 
